                <p>As an accomplished Operations Coordinator, my core focus is strategic planning and implementation for vNucleus. My extensive education and innate business knowledge allows me to streamline sales support and business operations using proven methods and technology. Identifying key issues, solving problems, and presenting solid alternatives for improvement are my areas of expertise.</p>
